## TerraformOS Download :
https://www.terraform.io/downloads

############## Install by downloading Terraform Binaries ##############
yum install -y wget unzip
wget -o https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/1.0.11/terraform_1.0.11_linux_arm64.zip
unzip ./terraform_1.0.11_linux_arm64.zip –d /usr/local/bin
terraform –v

############## Install using YUM Repo ##############

yum install -y yum-utils
yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/RHEL/hashicorp.repo  (For REDHAT)
sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/AmazonLinux/hashicorp.repo (For Amzon Linux)
yum -y install terraform
terraform -v 

NOTE: Since hashicorp repo is added, the other services i.e packer, vault, nomad and consul also can be installed by yum command.


